Also measured some coverage reports with `build_cov` (clang, `-fprofile-instr-generate -fcoverage-mapping`). [Before](https://frankomosh.github.io/fuzz-coverage/p2p-private-broadcast-coverage/before/index.html) and [After](https://frankomosh.github.io/fuzz-coverage/p2p-private-broadcast-coverage/after/index.html).

Some of the key coverage highlight diffs are as follows:

